graph LR
    KServe[KServe Operator<br/>serving.kserve.io]

    %% External Dependencies (Required/Recommended)
    KServe -->|"traffic routing<br/>VirtualServices<br/>DestinationRules"| Istio[Istio v1.x<br/>Optional/Recommended]
    KServe -->|"serverless<br/>autoscaling<br/>revision mgmt"| Knative[Knative Serving v1.x<br/>Optional - serverless mode]
    KServe -->|"TLS certificates<br/>webhook server"| CertManager[cert-manager v1.x<br/>Required]
    KServe -.->|"custom metrics<br/>autoscaling"| KEDA[KEDA v2.x<br/>Optional - raw deployment]
    KServe -.->|"metrics collection<br/>observability"| OTel[OpenTelemetry Operator v1beta1<br/>Optional]
    KServe -.->|"metrics scraping<br/>ServiceMonitor"| Prometheus[Prometheus Operator v1.x<br/>Optional]
    KServe -.->|"alternative ingress<br/>HTTPRoute"| GatewayAPI[Gateway API v1.x<br/>Optional]
    KServe -.->|"multi-node LLM<br/>distributed inference"| LWS[LeaderWorkerSet v1.x<br/>Optional - LLM only]

    %% Internal ODH/RHOAI Dependencies
    KServe -->|"mTLS<br/>traffic policies<br/>canary"| ServiceMesh[Service Mesh - OSSM<br/>Internal ODH]
    KServe -->|"external exposure<br/>Route resources"| Routes[OpenShift Routes<br/>Internal ODH]
    Dashboard[ODH Dashboard<br/>Internal ODH] -->|"UI management<br/>create/delete ISVC"| KServe
    KServe -->|"OAuth proxy<br/>metrics auth"| OAuth[OpenShift OAuth<br/>Internal ODH]
    KServe -->|"model storage<br/>versioning"| ModelRegistry[Model Registry<br/>Internal ODH]
    Pipelines[Data Science Pipelines<br/>Internal ODH] -->|"auto deploy models<br/>MLflow integration"| KServe
    KServe -.->|"authorization<br/>AuthorizationPolicy"| Authorino[Authorino<br/>Internal ODH - Optional]

    %% External Services
    KServe -->|"model artifacts<br/>AWS IAM/IRSA"| S3[S3 Storage<br/>s3.amazonaws.com]
    KServe -.->|"model artifacts<br/>Workload Identity"| GCS[Google Cloud Storage<br/>storage.googleapis.com]
    KServe -.->|"model artifacts<br/>Azure credentials"| Azure[Azure Blob Storage<br/>*.blob.core.windows.net]
    KServe -.->|"OCI model images<br/>modelcar feature"| Registry[Container Registries<br/>quay.io, gcr.io]
    KServe -->|"API operations<br/>resource CRUD"| K8sAPI[Kubernetes API Server<br/>6443/TCP]

